      class  Box
      A Box will have the function of managing a list of Transactions by storing the balance, the money spent and the money earned.
      class  DebitBox
      The DebitBox class represents a LoadBox with an interval that starts from the goal and ends at zero.
      class  LoadBox
      The LoadBox class extends the functionality of a Box allowing you to define a range in which the balance must be included.
      class  SaveBox
      The SaveBox class represents a LoadBox with an interval that starts from zero up to the target set.
      class  Wallet
      A Wallet will have the function of managing a list of Transactions by storing the balance, the money spent and the money earned.
